    <url>/2020/07/02/Win10%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Docker%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2Onlyoffice/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>安装docker</li>
<li>拉取镜像<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker pull onlyoffice/documentserver</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>启动服务<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -i -t -d -p 8072:80 onlyoffice/documentserver</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
